definitions.definition: ( intransitive , transitive , stative , Internet slang ) To be significantly more attractive than (someone or something); to dominate in appearance .
examples: His face mogs mine to hell and back .
This youngshit mogs me: I'm such a hon .

definitions.definition: ( transitive , stative , Internet slang , by extension ) To be superior to (something); to beat , outclass .

definitions.definition: ( intransitive , US , UK , dialectal ) To move or walk slowly; to trudge , amble ; ( more broadly ) to go .
( transitive , US , UK , dialectal , rare ) To cause to move ; to drive .
( transitive , intransitive ) In the game of costly colours : to exchange (a card ) with the dealer .
